    "We achieved average hit rates of 5.6%, 5.5%, and 5.1% for crystal structures, cryo-EM, and homology modeling, respectively.",
    "The number of projects using NMR structures is too small to make statistically-robust claims.",
    "(B) A comparison of hit rates observed for traditionally challenging target classes such as protein-protein interactions (PPI) and allosteric binding.",
    "Of the 296 projects, 72 targeted PPIs and 58 allosteric binding sites.",
    "The average hit rates were 6.4% and 5.8% for PPIs and allosteric binding, respectively."
